723159f-a.title: Manhattan: St. Nicholas Avenue - 182nd Street
723159f-a.text:
1445-47 St. Nicholas Avcnue (formerly Eleventh Avenue), west side,
between 182nd and 183rd Streets. This is a close-up of what
even twenty years earlier was suburban Wsshington Heights.
November 3, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
